  "text": "Elsewhere, the retention of a placenta increta fragment is manifested by the delayed onset, in relation to the abortion date, of a heterogeneous echogenic uterine mass. This interval varies from 2 weeks for Ju et al. [CITATION_1] to 3 years for Lim et al. [CITATION_2] .",
